sourcesContent: import React, { useState } from "react"; import { MDBNavbar, MDBNavbarBrand, MDBNavbarNav, MDBNavItem, MDBNavLink, MDBNavbarToggler, MDBCollapse, MDBDropdown, MDBDropdownToggle, MDBDropdownMenu, MDBDropdownItem, MDBIcon, MDBBtn } from "mdbreact"; import { BrowserRouter as Router, Redirect, Link } from 'react-router-dom'; function Navbar(props) { const [ isOpen, setState ] = useState(false) const toggleCollapse = () => { setState(!isOpen) } const handleLogout = () => { localStorage.removeItem('token') } return( <> PlacedIn Home Colleagues Interview Experiences Add profile Edit profile Your Posts Logout ) } export default Navbar
